Welcome to bridgething.

This is a Spotify Car Thing running mainline Linux + a community
userland.

Live status:
systemctl status bridgething-weston bridgething-chromium-kiosk
journalctl -u bridgething-chromium-kiosk -f

Iteration loop on the dev image:
bridgething-push-daemon ./build/bridgethingd
bridgething-push-webapp ./dist
/opt/bridgething/{daemon,webapps} - bind-mounted from settings,
survives bootslot swaps + OTA.
